	(text "Note:\n- LVDS_25 (2.5V) is supported in HR IO bank ONLY and requires VCCO to be powered at 2.5V\n- LVDS (1.8V ) is supported in HP IO bank ONLY and requires VCCO to be powered at 1.8V\n- You can use 1.8V LVDS as an input to HR IO bank and 2.5V LVDS as input to HP IO bank by meeting few criterias.\n- To see the criteria to be meat, please see following UG page #92 last paragraph.\nhttp://www.xilinx.com/support/documentation/user_guides/ug471_7Series_SelectIO.pdf"
